The <code>Screen</code> interface represents a screen, usually the one on which the current window is being rendered, and is obtained using <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/screen" title="The Window property screen returns a reference to the screen object associated with the window. The screen object, implementing the Screen interface, is a special object for inspecting properties of the screen on which the current window is being rendered."><code>window.screen</code></a>.